{"day":5,"topic":{"title":"Demonstrative Pronoun","emoji":"👉","cefr":"A1","difficulty":"beginner","type":"grammar"},"content":{"explanation":"\n**Demonstrative Pronouns — This/That/These/Those:**\n\n| Distance | Singular | Plural |\n|----------|----------|--------|\n| Near     | **This** | **These** |\n| Far      | **That** | **Those** |\n\n🇮🇳 यह मेरी किताब है। (पास)\n🇬🇧 **This** is my book.\n\n🇮🇳 वह घर बड़ा है। (दूर)\n🇬🇧 **That** house is big.\n\n🇮🇳 ये मेरे कपड़े हैं। (पास + plural)\n🇬🇧 **These** are my clothes.\n\n🇮🇳 वे पेड़ पुराने हैं। (दूर + plural)\n🇬🇧 **Those** trees are old.\n  ","rules":["This = nearby singular (यह/ये for singular)","That = far singular (वह far object)","These = nearby plural (ये सब पास वाले)","Those = far plural (वे सब दूर वाले)","This/That + singular verb (is/was)","These/Those + plural verb (are/were)"],"memoryTrick":"**TNTP: \"Two Near, Two Far\"**\n• Near: This (1), These (many)\n• Far: That (1), Those (many)\nYaad rakho: THiS = Small S = Singular | TheSE = Long SE = Several","examples":[{"hindi":"यह मेरा फोन है।","english":"This is my phone.","type":"This (near, singular)"},{"hindi":"वह एक बड़ा पेड़ है।","english":"That is a big tree.","type":"That (far, singular)"},{"hindi":"ये मेरी किताबें हैं।","english":"These are my books.","type":"These (near, plural)"},{"hindi":"वे लड़के शोर मचा रहे हैं।","english":"Those boys are making noise.","type":"Those (far, plural)"},{"hindi":"क्या यह सही है?","english":"Is this correct?","type":"Question with This"},{"hindi":"ये दिन बहुत अच्छे थे।","english":"Those days were very good.","type":"Those (past)"}],"mistakes":[{"wrong":"This books are good.","correct":"These books are good.","why":"Plural के लिए These"},{"wrong":"Those is my bag.","correct":"That is my bag.","why":"Singular far के लिए That"},{"wrong":"This are my friends.","correct":"These are my friends.","why":"Plural के साथ These"},{"wrong":"These book is heavy.","correct":"This book is heavy.","why":"Singular के साथ This"}],"speakingTips":["Around you jo bhi dikhe, wo sab describe karo (This is..., That is...)","Shopping karte waqt: \"I want this one\" / \"Can I see that one?\"","Office mein: \"This report is ready\" / \"Those files are pending\""]},"vocabulary":[{"id":1,"word":"Nearby","hindi":"पास में","ipa":"","example":"The school is nearby."},{"id":2,"word":"Distant","hindi":"दूर","ipa":"","example":"That is a distant city."},{"id":3,"word":"Adjacent","hindi":"बगल में","ipa":"","example":"This is the adjacent room."},{"id":4,"word":"Specific","hindi":"विशेष","ipa":"","example":"This specific topic is important."},{"id":5,"word":"Particular","hindi":"खास","ipa":"","example":"That particular student is brilliant."},{"id":6,"word":"Former","hindi":"पहला वाला","ipa":"","example":"The former option is better."},{"id":7,"word":"Latter","hindi":"बाद वाला","ipa":"","example":"I prefer the latter choice."},{"id":8,"word":"Above","hindi":"ऊपर वाला","ipa":"","example":"Those above rules apply here."}],"practice":[{"id":"d05-001","hindi":"यह मेरी कार है।","english":"This is my car.","alternatives":["this is my car."],"hint":"This = nearby singular","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-002","hindi":"वह एक पुरानी इमारत है।","english":"That is an old building.","alternatives":["that is an old building."],"hint":"That = far singular","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-003","hindi":"ये मेरी किताबें हैं।","english":"These are my books.","alternatives":["these are my books."],"hint":"These = nearby plural","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-004","hindi":"वे बच्चे हमारे स्कूल के हैं।","english":"Those children are from our school.","alternatives":["those kids are from our school."],"hint":"Those = far plural","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-005","hindi":"यह क्या है?","english":"What is this?","alternatives":["what is this?"],"hint":"What is this? (near)","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-006","hindi":"वह कौन है?","english":"Who is that?","alternatives":["who is that?"],"hint":"Who is that? (far)","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-007","hindi":"ये फूल बहुत सुंदर हैं।","english":"These flowers are very beautiful.","alternatives":["these flowers are very pretty."],"hint":"These + plural + are","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-008","hindi":"वे पहाड़ बहुत ऊँचे हैं।","english":"Those mountains are very high.","alternatives":["those mountains are very tall."],"hint":"Those + plural + are + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-009","hindi":"क्या यह तुम्हारा फ़ोन है?","english":"Is this your phone?","alternatives":["is this your mobile?"],"hint":"Is this your + noun?","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-010","hindi":"वह मेरा घर नहीं है।","english":"That is not my house.","alternatives":["that isn't my house.","that is not my home."],"hint":"That is not + my + noun","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-011","hindi":"यह समस्या बड़ी है।","english":"This problem is big.","alternatives":["this issue is big."],"hint":"This + noun + is + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-012","hindi":"ये सेब मीठे हैं।","english":"These apples are sweet.","alternatives":["these apples taste sweet."],"hint":"These + plural + are + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-013","hindi":"वे लड़के शोर मचा रहे हैं।","english":"Those boys are making noise.","alternatives":["those boys are being noisy."],"hint":"Those + noun + are + verb+ing","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-014","hindi":"यह सच्चाई है।","english":"This is the truth.","alternatives":["this is true.","this is the reality."],"hint":"This is the + noun","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-015","hindi":"वह मेरी गलती थी।","english":"That was my mistake.","alternatives":["that was my fault."],"hint":"That was my + noun","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-016","hindi":"ये तस्वीरें बहुत अच्छी हैं।","english":"These pictures are very nice.","alternatives":["these photos are very beautiful."],"hint":"These + noun + are + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-017","hindi":"वे पेड़ बहुत पुराने हैं।","english":"Those trees are very old.","alternatives":["those trees are quite old."],"hint":"Those + noun + are + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-018","hindi":"क्या यह सही है?","english":"Is this correct?","alternatives":["is this right?"],"hint":"Is this + adjective?","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-019","hindi":"यह मेरी ज़िम्मेदारी है।","english":"This is my responsibility.","alternatives":["this is my duty."],"hint":"This is my + noun","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-020","hindi":"वे दिन बहुत अच्छे थे।","english":"Those days were very good.","alternatives":["those were good days."],"hint":"Those days were + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-021","hindi":"यह मौका मत गँवाओ।","english":"Do not miss this opportunity.","alternatives":["don't miss this chance.","do not waste this opportunity."],"hint":"Don't miss this + noun","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-022","hindi":"ये सवाल बहुत कठिन हैं।","english":"These questions are very difficult.","alternatives":["these questions are very hard."],"hint":"These + noun + are + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-023","hindi":"वह बहुत दूर है।","english":"That is very far.","alternatives":["that place is very far."],"hint":"That is + very + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-024","hindi":"यह रास्ता सही है।","english":"This is the right way.","alternatives":["this is the correct path."],"hint":"This is the right + noun","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-025","hindi":"वे नियम पुराने हो गए हैं।","english":"Those rules are outdated.","alternatives":["those rules are old now."],"hint":"Those + noun + are + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-026","hindi":"ये फल बहुत ताज़े हैं।","english":"These fruits are very fresh.","alternatives":["these fruits are quite fresh."],"hint":"These + noun + are + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-027","hindi":"यह काम कल तक हो जाएगा।","english":"This work will be done by tomorrow.","alternatives":["this will be completed by tomorrow."],"hint":"This + will be + done + by","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-028","hindi":"वह लड़की मेरी बहन की दोस्त है।","english":"That girl is my sister's friend.","alternatives":["that girl is a friend of my sister."],"hint":"That + noun + is + possessive","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-029","hindi":"ये मेरे सपने हैं।","english":"These are my dreams.","alternatives":["these are my goals."],"hint":"These are my + plural noun","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-030","hindi":"वह एक ऐतिहासिक पल था।","english":"That was a historic moment.","alternatives":["that was a historical moment."],"hint":"That was a + adjective + noun","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-031","hindi":"यह मेरा पसंदीदा गाना है।","english":"This is my favourite song.","alternatives":["this is my favorite song."],"hint":"This is my favourite + noun","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-032","hindi":"वे कपड़े बहुत महँगे हैं।","english":"Those clothes are very expensive.","alternatives":["those clothes cost a lot."],"hint":"Those + noun + are + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-033","hindi":"क्या ये तुम्हारे बच्चे हैं?","english":"Are these your children?","alternatives":["are these your kids?"],"hint":"Are these your + noun?","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-034","hindi":"वह इमारत बहुत पुरानी है।","english":"That building is very old.","alternatives":["that building is quite old."],"hint":"That + noun + is + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-035","hindi":"यह मेरा आखिरी मौका है।","english":"This is my last chance.","alternatives":["this is my final chance."],"hint":"This is my + adjective + noun","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-036","hindi":"ये आदतें बदलनी होंगी।","english":"These habits need to change.","alternatives":["these habits must be changed."],"hint":"These + noun + need to + verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-037","hindi":"वह खबर सच नहीं है।","english":"That news is not true.","alternatives":["that news isn't true."],"hint":"That + noun + is not + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d05-038","hindi":"ये जूते बहुत आरामदायक हैं।","english":"These shoes are very comfortable.","alternatives":["these shoes feel very comfortable."],"hint":"These + noun + are + adjective","explanation":""},{"