leted by tomorrow."]},{"id":"d05-028-test","hindi":"वह लड़की मेरी बहन की दोस्त है।","english":"That girl is my sister's friend.","alternatives":["that girl is a friend of my sister."]},{"id":"d05-029-test","hindi":"ये मेरे सपने हैं।","english":"These are my dreams.","alternatives":["these are my goals."]},{"id":"d05-030-test","hindi":"वह एक ऐतिहासिक पल था।","english":"That was a historic moment.","alternatives":["that was a historical moment."]},{"id":"d05-031-test","hindi":"यह मेरा पसंदीदा गाना है।","english":"This is my favourite song.","alternatives":["this is my favorite song."]},{"id":"d05-032-test","hindi":"वे कपड़े बहुत महँगे हैं।","english":"Those clothes are very expensive.","alternatives":["those clothes cost a lot."]},{"id":"d05-033-test","hindi":"क्या ये तुम्हारे बच्चे हैं?","english":"Are these your children?","alternatives":["are these your kids?"]},{"id":"d05-034-test","hindi":"वह इमारत बहुत पुरानी है।","english":"That building is very old.","alternatives":["that building is quite old."]},{"id":"d05-035-test","hindi":"यह मेरा आखिरी मौका है।","english":"This is my last chance.","alternatives":["this is my final chance."]},{"id":"d05-036-test","hindi":"ये आदतें बदलनी होंगी।","english":"These habits need to change.","alternatives":["these habits must be changed."]},{"id":"d05-037-test","hindi":"वह खबर सच नहीं है।","english":"That news is not true.","alternatives":["that news isn't true."]},{"id":"d05-038-test","hindi":"ये जूते बहुत आरामदायक हैं।","english":"These shoes are very comfortable.","alternatives":["these shoes feel very comfortable."]},{"id":"d05-039-test","hindi":"क्या वह तुम्हारी कलम है?","english":"Is that your pen?","alternatives":["is that pen yours?"]},{"id":"d05-040-test","hindi":"यह हमारी आखिरी उम्मीद है।","english":"This is our last hope.","alternatives":["this is our only hope."]}]}